Facebook 3.2.3~core2

	* [Security] Use the new systemlog instead of security log and some minor documentation updates.
	* Better handling of inactive and deactivated users.
	* New support for authentication icons.
	* Facebook is updated to use the new Core authentication features.
	* Extension on the UserAuth API, renderLogin; add the ability to change Form options on execution of
	  the method.
	* Some auth-driver compatibility fixes for Facebook.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@eval.bz>  Sat, 22 Mar 2014 14:56:46 -0400

Facebook 3.2.3~core1

	* Update to newest version of the Facebook API from upstream.
	* Hide the appropriate facebook user configs from the interface.
	* Facebook needs to use the new Auth driver register system too.
	* Implement the new userauth driver in the Facebook component.
	* Bump the copyright date to 2014.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@eval.bz>  Thu, 02 Jan 2014 11:01:38 -0500

